cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CL 

This paper deals with visual recognition for fashion images, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). It also involves machine learning techniques for classification, which falls under the categories of multimedia (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of hierarchical annotations, which is a common topic in information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
